law.text: The center of the waters aforesaid shall be deemed to be as represented on the county maps issued under authority of the Laws of Maryland, 1896, Chapter 51, and the Laws of Maryland, 1898, Chapter 129, and said maps shall be admissible as evidence as to the location of the boundary or boundaries aforesaid.
